SpliceInterInfo has a new attribute: 'chim_class' that correspond to the chimera class from 1 to 4. This class is now outputed on both SAM and .chimera files (documentation has been updated). An other improvement concerns the chimeric alignement given for a class 2 chimera. Since it is a colinnear alignement we do not use the '0N' nomenclature anymore.
